{"tid":2240234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"菲律賓著名blogger投訴瑞典餐廳「習蝙蝠」海報種族歧視 令其香港朋友不安 迫畫家撤走及道歉","createTime":"2020-10-12T13:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T11:26:31.000Z","uid":358086,"like":6,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"98c5c09b8858dd9826fc1c0346e1612ff7f2e860","tid":2240234,"uid":358086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T13:37:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a7uLfE4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa7uLfE4.jpg&h=17a623c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾任《全美超模大賽》主持、菲律賓著名時裝blogger Bryanboy日前於ig上發文，指佢喺瑞典斯德哥爾摩一間餐廳食飯嘅時候，發現餐廳貼滿「畫到塊面好黃、有蝙蝠耳仔」嘅習近平海報，上面寫住「BAT MAN」字眼。Bryanboy表示當時餐廳裡面只有佢同朋友2個係亞裔，雖然已經嗌咗嘢食但都好想馬上離開餐廳，又提出武肺以來令佢同好多朋友都飽受歧視。<br />\n<br />\n海報創作者「ironartworks」得悉後亦隨即喺ig發文，再三慎重向所有因為呢張poster而受冒犯嘅人致歉，並解釋佢一直以來嘅創作都係以諷刺極權者為重點，今次亦只係想諷刺中共同習近平引致武肺爆發，無意製造種族歧視嘅言論。而餐廳亦對張貼作品令人不安致歉，並將海報撤走。<br />\n<br />\n根據BBC訪問，Bryanboy就對「ironartworks」嘅回應就感到不滿，覺得對方並非道歉，指責佢唔知自己嘅作品會引發啲咩效應係一種「無知」；而海報設計者則表示認為今次事件係「取消文化」嘅例子，意指知名人士因某啲被指冒犯嘅行為而受到公眾抵制，因為呢張海報已經喺當地展示咗幾個月，喺餐廳內亦張貼咗一個月，從未收到有關投訴，認為呢種「取消文化」對社會嘅影響遠比藝術創作帶來嘅影響更加大。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：100毛<br />\n<br />\nBBC | IG/Bryanboy、ironartworks<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">個愛支菲律賓人係IG同Twitter不斷del走香港人留言</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/bryanboy/status/1314990170605850625?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fbryanboy%2Fstatus%2F1314990170605850625%3Fs%3D20&d=W9k3bdIekjUozLnTtmc2Vy%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=624030a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fbryanboy%2Fstatus%2F1314990170605850625%3Fs%3D20&h=38ed30e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/bryanboy/status/1314990170605850625?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CGLA7lPBLwB/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCGLA7lPBLwB%2F&d=W9k3bdIekjUozLnTtmc2Vy%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=319cc0f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCGLA7lPBLwB%2F&h=4c850319\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CGLA7lPBLwB/</a>"},{"pid":"d005b8b7878e8e89e679679b6728d87e0bb52386","tid":2240234,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T13:40:15.000Z","msg":"香港黃店夠唔夠膽貼返相同POSTER?"},{"pid":"8ff39233d785a3293114d4260e969d44b1106062","tid":2240234,"uid":63157,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T13:41:39.000Z","msg":"Xenophobia呢個字絕對係比佢地濫用<br />\n政治漫畫不嬲都係咁畫<br />\n諷刺個領導人=諷刺全個亞洲既人??"},{"pid":"c0a2f31994eabedaf539ca4e8a2a3c3b7797a6b0","tid":2240234,"uid":42422,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T13:43:37.000Z","msg":"個香港朋友定中國朋友黎呀？<br />\n成個撈閪樣咁"},{"pid":"8e84d2d9c7ccc91a3f273554f61f0b74ebbb3e29","tid":2240234,"uid":273218,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T13:45:12.000Z","msg":"撐共先係種族歧視"},{"pid":"23ab6e7e0ead427efc6ef3951dd08807c9ca3e09","tid":2240234,"uid":286897,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T13:45:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a97274a05d559f3693a3852b303931c94286fc09","tid":2240234,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T13:47:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2f9a6a4ed0e056bb6b3e1793c5b997fd